    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to start and has a noticeable knock, while the transmission slips frequently. Cosmetically, there is visible rust on the rocker panels, several large dents on the passenger side, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn. It is best suited as a project car for a dedicated restorer or as a donor for parts.",
