    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this diamond in the rough! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its peak, it\u2019s the perfect opportunity for a handy driver or someone looking for a budget-friendly entry into car ownership. With a little love and some dedicated TLC, you can breathe new life into this vehicle and make it your own!",
