    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolute mint condition and babied since day one. No scratches, no dents, and that new car smell is still going strong! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve kept it garaged and stayed on top of every single service. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and ready for a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
