      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a collector-grade example of the final analog M-car. At its heart is the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance: the rear subframe has been reinforced, rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells, and the VANOS system overhauled with Beisan components. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, with all bushings and ball joints showing zero deflection. The exterior retains its original factory depth with no swirl marks, and the interior leather remains supple with no bolster compression. A truly turn-key specimen for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
