      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-quality specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively by certified technicians. This sale includes all original keys, the owner\u2019s manual set, and the original window sticker. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
